---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Our Review Methodology | Best AI Website Builder"
  description="Learn how we test and score AI website builders. Our transparent methodology ensures fair, unbiased reviews."
>
  <article class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-12 prose prose-lg">
    <h1>Our Review Methodology</h1>
    <p>We evaluate every AI website builder using a consistent, transparent scoring system across four key dimensions.</p>

    <h2>Scoring Criteria</h2>

    <h3>1. Ease of Use (30%)</h3>
    <p>We measure how quickly a complete beginner can go from sign-up to a published website. We time the process, count the number of steps, and evaluate the quality of AI-generated output on the first attempt.</p>

    <h3>2. Features (30%)</h3>
    <p>We evaluate the breadth and depth of features including AI capabilities, template quality, ecommerce support, integrations, and CMS functionality.</p>

    <h3>3. Pricing & Value (20%)</h3>
    <p>We assess the pricing structure, free plan limitations, and whether the paid plans offer good value relative to competitors.</p>

    <h3>4. SEO Friendliness (20%)</h3>
    <p>We check for built-in SEO tools, clean HTML output, Core Web Vitals performance, and mobile responsiveness.</p>

    <h2>Independence Policy</h2>
    <p>Our editorial team makes all scoring decisions independently. Affiliate relationships do not influence review scores or rankings. We disclose all affiliate relationships transparently.</p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
